org.apache.ddlutils.io
Class WaitingObject

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.ddlutils.io.WaitingObject

public class WaitingObject
extends Object

Represents an object waiting for insertion into the database. Is used by the DataToDatabaseSink to insert the objects in the correct order according to their foreign keys.

Version:
$Revision: 289996 $
